Now go to this site: [url=http://www.statman.info/conversions/hexadecimal.html]http://www.statman.info/conversions/hexadecimal.html[/url]

Enter in 112590872
press to Heximal(6b60018)
enter in 06b6
Press to Decimal
Animation File :1718

Enter in 0018
Press to Decimal
Animation frame:24


Total out come
112590872
06b6 0018
1718   24

Now Do 112590872 - 24 = 112590872

that means you can do everything of this list - 112590872 to get the 100% order


Thats it so simple is that. Ask any questions
